Archive.description: Represents an EMIL Product archive file.

Artifact.description: Each artifact represents a single report for the given time period designated by the EMIL metadata.

Exception.description: Represents any exception encountered while access API endpoints.

Product.description: Represents an EMIL Product, which includes its metadata along with all Artifact information.

ProductHistory.description: Each archive represents a single EMIL Product archive (zip file).

ProductHistoryMetadata.description: Represents record and paging summary for the specified query results.

QueryMetadata.description: Represents query parameter summary for the specified query results.

Report.description: Represents report data search results from any EMIL artifact report query.

ReportMetadata.description: Represents metadata for the specified object.

ResultMetadata.description: Represents record and paging summary for the specified query results.
